{"tid":170640,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有餵開流浪貓","createTime":"2017-03-24T20:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T18:03:51.000Z","uid":24976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c998d1fca0786047b0dbaaff92788b1e53ebc0c","tid":170640,"uid":24976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T20:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開始係荃灣餵"},{"pid":"eedbd871e31a46e3f96d86d8a8601fa56e9a6d5b","tid":170640,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T20:54:47.000Z","msg":"以前有 細妹係屋企樓下個垃圾房見到2隻浪浪貓<br />\n跟住我就慣左成日落去喂佢地<br />\n但果陣我驚比人投訴浪浪會人道毁滅<br />\n跟住好蠢咁留左自己電話比佢地<br />\n話佢地比人捉可以搵我 我幫手搵貓義工<br />\n點知我就咁岩去左旅行果陣比人投訴<br />\n去完旅行番去貓仔就無曬<br />\n內疚左好耐...對唔住係我蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8d721ab63d0c69c38c57a3d9cbbc07c73d076c","tid":170640,"uid":96628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T21:37:43.000Z","msg":"泊開車個停車場好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但好驚人<br />\n驚人都好，有啲餵開貓嘅阿姐竏有啲大陸人專捉啲唔驚人嗰啲來食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自此好擔心佢地，同時佢地驚我我個心會好過啲"},{"pid":"ef9f9eaf3842a79accf29cac47cc76a6d88e907a","tid":170640,"uid":96628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T21:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泊開車個停車場好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但好驚人<br />\n驚人都好，有啲餵開貓嘅阿姐<span style=\"color: red;\">竏</span>有啲大陸人專捉啲唔驚人嗰啲來食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自此好擔心佢地，同時佢地驚我我個心會好過啲</blockquote><br />\n話"},{"pid":"fa02f9ea5c7031e8c90f1ccd92b642edf1c4187a","tid":170640,"uid":51726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T00:37:02.000Z","msg":"樓主係荃灣邊度餵？<br />\n我之前係果邊嘅公園餵左排<br />\n俾人話我違反遊樂場條例 話我再去就告我<br />\n我驚佢地會搵人搞啲貓 所以冇再去餵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但果度有隻貓好瘦 又好怕人怕貓 依家餵唔到佢唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1da2a7e928e638a66a8c11b91961c4eb38014f4","tid":170640,"uid":74002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:18:38.000Z","msg":"荃灣餵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daef11d93ad9a000accad7c6c8b88bcbc68d5238","tid":170640,"uid":24976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係荃灣邊度餵？<br />\n我之前係果邊嘅公園餵左排<br />\n俾人話我違反遊樂場條例 話我再去就告我<br />\n我驚佢地會搵人搞啲貓 所以冇再去餵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但果度有隻貓好瘦 又好怕人怕貓 依家餵唔到佢唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咩公園？<br />\n我係德華公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff55e713d6b861682f1e2b7b4cbbea77e229bd8","tid":170640,"uid":87579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T21:26:47.000Z","msg":"前排一路樓下都好多<br />\n但而家唔見哂咁濟<br />\n我懷疑係有人專登放狗咬死佢地或者放有毒既野比佢地食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c734e29954f4b0273ebfaaccd677b6fae8d438","tid":170640,"uid":50290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T21:53:43.000Z","msg":"浪浪"},{"pid":"37ce789b49060facf4622d657d268cb5b6a21261","tid":170640,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"樓下有人餵 <br />\n唔駛我餵<br />\n我只係同佢地玩"},{"pid":"4597a58cb7ea051533c1db2a392afa344c46b5bc","tid":170640,"uid":51726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T08:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主係荃灣邊度餵？<br />\n我之前係果邊嘅公園餵左排<br />\n俾人話我違反遊樂場條例 話我再去就告我<br />\n我驚佢地會搵人搞啲貓 所以冇再去餵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但果度有隻貓好瘦 又好怕人怕貓 依家餵唔到佢唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咩公園？<br />\n我係德華公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係德華呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪中間堆假石 果度有幾隻<br />\n我見夜晚有阿姨餵 但有隻特別細同瘦 驚左啲大貓 又怕人 焗住要走入去餵"},{"pid":"2380ee9bff7486d4137529559a80a0e34cb91995","tid":170640,"uid":74002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T08:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主係荃灣邊度餵？<br />\n我之前係果邊嘅公園餵左排<br />\n俾人話我違反遊樂場條例 話我再去就告我<br />\n我驚佢地會搵人搞啲貓 所以冇再去餵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但果度有隻貓好瘦 又好怕人怕貓 依家餵唔到佢唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咩公園？<br />\n我係德華公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係德華呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪中間堆假石 果度有幾隻<br />\n我見夜晚有阿姨餵 但有隻特別細同瘦 驚左啲大貓 又怕人 焗住要走入去餵</blockquote><br />\n唔好講咁details<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c32577a5ed02a007c2b2315cede6d108a0f9232","tid":170640,"uid":51726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T09:02:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主係荃灣邊度餵？<br />\n我之前係果邊嘅公園餵左排<br />\n俾人話我違反遊樂場條例 話我再去就告我<br />\n我驚佢地會搵人搞啲貓 所以冇再去餵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但果度有隻貓好瘦 又好怕人怕貓 依家餵唔到佢唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咩公園？<br />\n我係德華公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係德華呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\